
This is a UDP server that runs on port 32000 transceiving everything it receives to I2C bus /dev/i2c-0.

1. Get OpenWRT source code and compile the toolchain:
    https://dev.openwrt.org/wiki/GetSource
    http://wiki.openwrt.org/doc/howto/build

2. Edit env.sh and set TOOLCHAIN variable to your OpenWRT cross compilation toolchain directory

3. Export variables from env.sh: 
    . ./env.sh

4. Simply run "make"

